summary:
Experienced Transport Manager in charge of Road Freight Transport within EU, EEA countries and UK with the aim to fulfill our customers needs and requirements .

Skilled in different industries in EU, UK and Middle East. Automotive - E-commerce - Air cargo - Time Critical Shipments to Vessels - Express - Pharma and Oil shipping .

Available 24/24 , 7/7 with experienced and motivated. 

Contact : dana.kolencikova@erfolg.sk
